      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN CARAMEL (1) goes very well at the course and distance with two wins and a placing from six starts. Below best last time at Richmond Straight (18.07) in a Grade 5, finishing a 4.5 lengths fifth. Looks a key chance on best form. WIGHTON BANNER (6) turned in a better effort at this track last start, finishing second behind CHRISY'S WISH (18.49) in a Grade 5. Has the pace to be prominent. Must be included in calculations. CHEEKY SLOY (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing third (18.90) at this track. Expecting another good run. CHRISY'S WISH (7) won as favourite last time and is a major player again.",
